{"tid":2251902,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"香港電台：回應持中資銀行帳戶　特朗普一方只繳稅不涉任何交易","createTime":"2020-10-21T06:17:43.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-21T10:08:55.000Z","uid":290404,"like":8,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"a13cf58a8f7fe2dc7d68f378797c289965cc30cd","tid":2251902,"uid":290404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-21T06:17:43.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1555910-20201021.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1555910-20201021.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=URyNnIoFf2HINYay4fd4QR3udkpk2VnOHMKOPHAv%2FIQ%3D&h=1ded9161\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1555910-20201021.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=d0af0692\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1555910-20201021.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong>《紐約時報》報道，美國總統特朗普持有一個中資銀行的帳戶，但未有申報相關資料。</strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong>報道說，稅務紀錄顯示，特朗普名下的「特朗普國際酒店管理公司」，在2013至2015年，透過有關中資銀行帳戶，繳付超過18萬8千美元地方稅款。</strong><br />\n<br />\n特朗普一方承認擁有中資銀行的帳戶，他的律師表示，有關帳戶是公司在中國設立辦事處後開設，目的是探索亞洲酒店業潛力，強調帳戶是用作繳納中國的稅款，不涉及任何交易或商業活動，而有關中國辦事處自2015年起就停止運作，雖然帳戶仍然開設，但未用作其他用途。"},{"pid":"c61de54a859889f0e84031b5bd428883d39870cd","tid":2251902,"uid":188176,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-10-21T06:19:01.000Z","msg":"其實有個戶口有乜咁奇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c9f370a408ee62bdc6550aeb7fe6859d3074fad","tid":2251902,"uid":290404,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"c61de54a859889f0e84031b5bd428883d39870cd","tid":2251902,"uid":188176,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-10-21T06:19:01.000Z","msg":"其實有個戶口有乜咁奇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-21T06:20:07.000Z","msg":"擺明就係抹黑"},{"pid":"a0606ea7dd414957d5a62f93cfda4f94d060c2d2","tid